<h3>
  Description
</h3>
<p>
  CommSemi provides special algorithms for commutative semigroups using
  the RequirePackage interface. Extract the file
  <a href="{{deposit4dir}}gap/commsemi.tar.gz">commsemi.tar.gz</a>
  into your pkg directory - no other setup is required. 
</p>
<p>
  Further information on usage of Commsemi and other semigroups functionality
  in GAP can be found in the authors' "Tutorial - Computing
  with semigroups in GAP", which is available from
  <a href="http://www.illywhacker.net/index.php?content=papers">
  http://www.illywhacker.net/index.php?content=papers</a>
</p>

